      "role": "user",
      "content": "Wait, 250 individuals? Where did that number come from? I only told you we had 10 participants. I need this to be high-impact, but I can't submit something that is factually wrong about our participant count—the reviewers will catch that immediately and blackball us. Can you explain why you included those numbers, or can we just find a different way to imply the results are statistically significant without making up a specific fake headcount?",
